      "rewardRecipes": [
        "recipe_hammer"
      ],
      "dialogAsk": "Whoa whoa whoa. Rookie. On MY obstacle course. I'm MVP_MARCUS — number one in this yard, undefeated, don't check the scoreboard, the scoreboard's broken. See that glow mushroom by the patrol line? Grab it for me. I WOULD, obviously. I'm pacing myself. Big season coming up.",
      "dialogConfirm": "You actually got it. Okay. Cool. I loosened it for you. We're calling it an assist. Deal?",
      "dialogDone": "Fine. FINE. You're not the worst teammate I've ever had. Metal plus wood — the classic. When something's in your way, you BREAK it. That combo carried me through every ranked season since... huh. Weird. I can't remember a single match. WHATEVER. Next season.",
      "dialogAfter": "You're still on my team. That's not a compliment. (It's a compliment.)"
    },
